node.text: 🥤🍊🥥🍉🍋 Saturday (tomorrow) August 7th, we’re having our Drive In sour party in the taproom! These are the 4packs we’ll have available - four sour flavors, half with lactose. All delish! $14 for each 4pack (yes these are limited and taproom only, so that’s that! no singles). We’ll have all four flavors on tap as well til they float. Doors at 12pm. Wristbands til 5pm. Two food trucks. Live music. Let’s rage. Oh and happy fireball friday! Let’s kill it. #lemonberry #orangecream #watermeloncandy #pacificwaves #fireballfriday

node.text: Welp, everyone seems to be digging the girl scout and the mega fast so far. “andes mint” is a very accurate description for girl scout. There weren’t too many reviews for mega fast, so just threw caveman sponge bob on there. If you have an untappd, let us know what you think. Or comment below. Thanks to Rob and Sean for the pics. Cheers! #girlscout #jellyfish

node.text: This Saturday, August 7th 12-5pm: Drive-In Sour Beer party! Mark it down! We’re tapping up these four different fruited sours. There will be a limited amount of mixed 4packs to-go for $14 (yep, taproom only this year). Our buddy @matt_nestor_music will be out back with his guitar. And the buddies @funky.calavera and doghouse food trailer will be out back with their delicious grub. Hope to see yall there! Cheers! #martinhouse #fortworth #fortworthtx #seefortworth #eatfortworth #hearfortworth #orangecream #watermeloncandy #lemonberry #pacificwaves #dfw
